title: AFSCME Clerical Union Collective Bargaining Agreements for the Last 10 Years

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Minnesota Government Data Practices Act, I hereby request the following records:

I am requesting your AFSCME Clerical Unit Collective Bargaining Agreements for the last 10 years, including the following years:
1. AFSCME Clerical Unit Collective Bargaining Agreement of 2015
2. AFSCME Clerical Unit Collective Bargaining Agreement of 2016
3. AFSCME Clerical Unit Collective Bargaining Agreement of 2017
4. AFSCME Clerical Unit Collective Bargaining Agreement of 2018
5. AFSCME Clerical Unit Collective Bargaining Agreement of 2019
6. AFSCME Clerical Unit Collective Bargaining Agreement of 2020
7. AFSCME Clerical Unit Collective Bargaining Agreement of 2021
8. AFSCME Clerical Unit Collective Bargaining Agreement of 2022
9. AFSCME Clerical Unit Collective Bargaining Agreement of 2023

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days.

communications.subject: Minnesota Government Data Practices Act Request: Official Posted Job Description Request
communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Minnesota Government Data Practices Act, I hereby request the following records:

I am requesting from your Office of Human Resources all official job descriptions posted and used for hiring personnel under job requisition #302507. I seek the records detailing unit-assigned responsibilities and required and preferred qualifications. This request explicitly excludes general job classification descriptions.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days.
